                        <p class="dark-gray">Showing @(Model.PageIndex * Model.PageSize - Model.PageSize + 1) - @(Model.PageIndex * Model.PageSize > Model.Count ? Model.Count : Model.PageIndex * Model.PageSize) of @Model.Count Results</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

